subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Jane Park, the 2004 United States amateur champion, completed a wire-to-wire victory at the L.P.G.A. Final Qualifying Tournament in Daytona Beach, Fla. Seventeen players earned full 2008 playing status. Park had a 17-under-par 274 total.
